'''爱德华·约翰·大卫·“艾迪”·雷德梅尼'''，[[大英帝國勳章|OBE]]（{{lang-en|'''Edward John David "Eddie" Redmayne'''}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.debretts.com/people/biographies/browse/r/26029/Edward%20John%20David%20(Eddie)%20REDMAYNE.aspx |title=Eddie Redmayne, Esq Authorised Biography – Debrett<nowiki>’</nowiki>s People of Today, Eddie Redmayne, Esq Profile |publisher=Debretts.com |date=1982-01-06 |accessdate=2011-01-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206105917/http://www.debretts.com/people/biographies/browse/r/26029/Edward%20John%20David%20(Eddie)%20REDMAYNE.aspx |archivedate=2012-02-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/individual/1177117 |title=BFI | Film & TV Database | REDMAYNE, Eddie |publisher=Ftvdb.bfi.org.uk |date=2009-04-16 |accessdate=2011-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022075522/http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/individual/1177117 |archive-date=2012-10-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，{{bd|1982年|1月6日|||Redmayne, Eddie}}）<ref name="GQ">{{cite news|title=Made in Britain|publisher=gqonline.it|url=http://www.gqonline.it/cont/060sty/062pro/0611/0200/default.asp?np=2|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071121100618/http://www.gqonline.it/cont/060sty/062pro/0611/0200/default.asp?np=2|archivedate=2007-11-21|accessdate=2012-03-03}}</ref>是一位[[英國|英國]]男[[演員|演員]]、[[模特兒|模特兒]]與[[歌手|歌手]]。

他於2000年代早期開展他的银幕事業，開始時他參與電視劇與電影的演出，其首部作品是《{{tsl|en|Like Minds|心智相投}}》。2010年，他繼續在劇院演出，於[[百老匯|百老匯]]的劇目《紅》最受注目，因此他獲得[[東尼獎|東尼獎]]的最佳劇場表現男配角。期後他於2014年由[[詹姆斯·马什|詹姆斯·马什]]執導的傳記電影《[[愛的萬物論|愛的萬物論]]》中飾演[[史蒂芬·霍金|史蒂芬·霍金]]，其演出備受肯定，並赢得[[金球獎|金球獎]]、[[第68屆英國電影學院獎|英國電影學院獎]]、[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]，以及[[第87届奧斯卡金像獎|第87届奧斯卡金像獎]]最佳男主角。

2015年，他獲英廷頒授[[英帝國官佐勳章|OBE勳銜]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/honours-list/11671979/Queens-Birthday-Honours-Van-Morrison-knighted.html|title=Queen's Birthday Honours: Van Morrison knighted|work=The Telegraph|date=2015-06-12|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128084848/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/honours-list/11671979/Queens-Birthday-Honours-Van-Morrison-knighted.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，他於電影《[[丹麥女孩|丹麥女孩]]》中演繹首個接受變性手術的[[莉莉·艾爾伯|莉莉·艾爾伯]]，使他再次獲得[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]、[[金球獎|金球獎]]、[[英國電影學院獎|英國電影學院獎]]及[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]最佳男主角提名。

==早期生活==
埃迪·雷德梅尼在1982年1月6日出生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/individual/1177117|title=Redmayne profile|publisher=Ftvdb.bfi.org.uk|date=2009-04-16|accessdate=2011-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022075522/http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/individual/1177117|archive-date=2012-10-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，他的曾祖父是{{link-en|李察·雷德梅尼|Richard Redmayne}}爵士，是土木和採礦工程師<ref name="news.moviefone.com">{{cite web|url=http://news.moviefone.com/2014/11/21/eddie-redmayne-facts|title=Eddie Redmayne Facts: 23 Things You (Probably) Don't Know About the 'Theory of Everything' Star|website=moviefone.com|date=2014-11-21|access-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121024126/http://news.moviefone.com/2014/11/21/eddie-redmayne-facts/|archive-date=2015-11-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，父親是一名商人，母親營運一家負責員工遷移服務的公司<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eddieredmayne.org/?p=733|title=Fast Eddie|publisher=Eddieredmayne.org|accessdate=2015-02-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129025547/http://www.eddieredmayne.org/?p=733|archivedate=2014-11-29}}</ref>。有一位哥哥和弟弟，以及一位同父異母的哥哥和姐姐<ref name="Eddie Redmayne interview">{{cite web|title=Eddie Redmayne interview|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/theatre/theatre-features/6614502/Eddie-Redmayne-interview.html|accessdate=2014-11-23|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009141341/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/theatre/theatre-features/6614502/Eddie-Redmayne-interview.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他有[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]、[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]、[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]及[[威爾士|威爾士]]的血統<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ethnicelebs.com/eddie-redmayne|title=Eddie Redmayne|publisher=ethnicelebs.com|date=2012-10-25|accessdate=2015-08-09|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503165452/https://ethnicelebs.com/eddie-redmayne|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

埃迪就讀於一所私立男校Colet Court，然後就讀[[伊頓公學|伊頓公學]]<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2952989/The-Oscar-outstanding-poshness-goes-Eddie-Redmayne-Brit-tipped-land-Academy-Award-week-privileged-think.html Redmayne tipped to land Academy Award] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2952989/The-Oscar-outstanding-poshness-goes-Eddie-Redmayne-Brit-tipped-land-Academy-Award-week-privileged-think.html |date=20160304075107 }}, dailymail.co.uk; accessed 23 February 2015.</ref>，並跟[[劍橋公爵威廉王子|威廉王子]]是同年級的同學，比演員[[汤姆·希德勒斯顿|湯姆·希德斯頓]]小一屆<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/entertainment/articles/2011-11/28/eddie-redmayne-week-with-marilyn-birdsong|title=Next Big Thing: Eddie Redmayne|website=gq-magazine.co.uk|date=2011-11-28|accessdate=2012-12-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130105223601/http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/entertainment/articles/2011-11/28/eddie-redmayne-week-with-marilyn-birdsong|archivedate=2013-01-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2096243/Prince-William-Birdsongs-Eddie-Redmayne-pictured-Eton-wearing-wacky-waistcoats.html|title=Prince William with the Birdsong heart-throb and fellow Eton prefects... and some VERY wacky waistcoats|work=[[The_Daily_Mail|The Daily Mail]]|date=2012-02-04|accessdate=2012-12-19|location=London|first1=Christian|last1=Gysin|first2=Ryan|last2=Kisiel|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306065924/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2096243/Prince-William-Birdsongs-Eddie-Redmayne-pictured-Eton-wearing-wacky-waistcoats.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來他在[[劍橋大學三一學院|劍橋大學三一學院]]修讀[[藝術史|藝術史]]，並於2003年以二級榮譽的成績畢業<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/nov/19/eddie-redmayne-marilyn-monroe|title=Eddie Redmayne: the loneliness of being a hot young actor|publisher=Guardian.co.uk|accessdate=2012-01-15|archive-date=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625074427/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/nov/19/eddie-redmayne-marilyn-monroe|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==職業生涯==
===模特兒===
在成為全職演員之前，埃迪·雷德梅尼是英國品牌[[巴寶莉|巴寶莉]]的模特兒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3081721/Eddie-Redmayne-spruces-new-Burberry-shoot.html|title=Eddie Redmayne spruces new Burberry shoot|author=Kate Thomas|date=2015-05-14|publisher=DailyMail|accessdate=2016-02-08|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120074022/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3081721/Eddie-Redmayne-spruces-new-Burberry-shoot.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/showbiz/news/a358344/eddie-redmayne-cara-delevingne-pose-for-burberry-videos-pictures.html|title=Eddie Redmayne, Cara Delevingne pose for Burberry - videos, pictures|publisher=Digitalspy.com.au|accessdate=2012-01-15|archive-date=2015-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005165711/http://www.digitalspy.com.au/showbiz/news/a358344/eddie-redmayne-cara-delevingne-pose-for-burberry-videos-pictures.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2012年9月出版的《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利場]]》，他獲選列入《年度全球最佳穿著》的名單<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/style/2012/09/the-2012-international-best-dressed-list#slide=45|title=Vanity Fair 2012 International Best Dressed List|work=[[Vanity_Fair_(magazine)|Vanity Fair]]|date=2012-07-31|accessdate=2012-09-10|archive-date=2012-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120911072916/http://www.vanityfair.com/style/2012/09/the-2012-international-best-dressed-list#slide=45|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，他獲[[GQ|GQ]]雜誌列入《50位最佳穿著的英國男士》第一位<ref>{{cite news|title=50 Best Dressed Men in Britain 2015|url=http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/style/articles/2015-01/05/best-dressed-men-2015|work=GQ|date=2015-01-05|accessdate=2015-02-23|archive-date=2015-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107145128/http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/style/articles/2015-01/05/best-dressed-men-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===舞台演出===
埃迪·雷德梅尼的首個舞台演出是《[[第十二夜|第十二夜]]》的維奧拉（Viola），在2002年於[[中殿律師學院|中殿律師學院]]演出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/theatre-dance/features/eddie-redmayne-the-darling-of-the-donmar-is-making-tracks-into-hollywood-1860155.html|title=Eddie Redmayne: The darling of the Donmar is making tracks into Hollywood|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=2010-01-07|accessdate=2015-03-06|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024173142/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/theatre-dance/features/eddie-redmayne-the-darling-of-the-donmar-is-making-tracks-into-hollywood-1860155.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他憑此劇於2004年獲得傑出新人獎。2005年，他再憑《[[山羊_(話劇)|山羊]]》獲得新演員獎<ref name="timesonline">{{cite news|title=Almost Famous|date=2005-05-26|work=[[The_Times|The Times]]|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/article/0,,14931-1627261_1,00.html}}</ref>。

2009年，埃迪為話劇《紅》於[[倫敦|倫敦]]演出，憑該劇於[[勞倫斯·奧立佛獎|勞倫斯·奧立佛獎]]奪得最佳男配角。他在[[百老匯|百老匯]]重演該劇，贏得[[東尼獎|東尼獎]]的最佳男主角。

===影視演出===
埃迪·雷德梅尼的首部電影作品為2006年的《{{link-en|心智相投|Like Minds}}》，是該電影的選角導演於《山羊》舞台劇時發現他。之後他相繼出演了《[[特務風雲：中情局誕生秘辛|特務風雲：中情局誕生秘辛]]》（2006年）、《{{link-en|浮華陷阱|Savage Grace}}》（2007年）、《[[華麗孽緣|華麗孽緣]]》（2008年）、《{{link-en|烽火家族情|Glorious 39}}》（2009年）與《[[鄉下人_(電影)|鄉下人]]》（2011年）。

他在2012年的歌舞電影《[[悲慘世界_(2012年電影)|悲慘世界]]》中飾演[[馬留斯·彭梅西|馬留斯·彭梅西]]<ref name="Redmayne">{{cite web|last=Jensen|first=Jeff|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/11/01/eddie-redmayne-les-miserables|title=Eddie Redmayne lands 'Les Miserables' role|publisher=Insidemovies.ew.com|accessdate=2015-02-23|archive-date=2014-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109233510/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/11/01/eddie-redmayne-les-miserables/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=83797|title=Les Miserables Adds Eddie Redmayne|publisher=Comingsoon.net|accessdate=2015-02-23|archive-date=2014-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109221535/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=83797|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，雷德梅尼在《[[愛的萬物論|愛的萬物論]]》中飾演[[史蒂芬·霍金|史蒂芬·霍金]]而有著突破性的演出，這使他贏得了[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]、[[英國電影學院獎|英國電影學院獎]]、[[金球獎|金球獎]]和[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Eddie Redmayne wins first Oscar for 'Theory of Everything'|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/23/us-awards-oscars-actor-idUSKBN0LR0AF20150223|accessdate=2015-03-07|publisher=Reuters|date=2015-02-23|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926134621/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/23/us-awards-oscars-actor-idUSKBN0LR0AF20150223|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Watch Eddie Redmayne's Charming Best Actor Acceptance Speech at the Oscars|url=http://time.com/3716096/oscars-2015-best-actor|publisher=Time|accessdate=2015-03-07|archive-date=2015-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306205501/http://time.com/3716096/oscars-2015-best-actor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年，雷德梅尼出演了[[華卓斯基姐妹|華卓斯基姐妹]]的科幻片《[[朱比特崛起|朱比特崛起]]》而獲得[[金酸莓獎|金酸莓獎]]，因為該片獲得普遍負面的評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/661257-razzie-awards-2016-winners-announced#/slide/1|title=Razzie Awards 2016 Winners Announced - ComingSoon.net|date=2016-02-27|publisher=|accessdate=2016-11-21|archive-date=2016-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311102520/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/661257-razzie-awards-2016-winners-announced#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，他亦因《[[丹麥女孩|丹麥女孩]]》而提名了[[奧斯卡最佳男主角獎|奧斯卡最佳男主角獎]]。

2016年，他在《[[哈利波特|哈利波特]]》外傳同名小說改編成電影《[[怪獸與牠們的產地_(電影)|怪獸與牠們的產地]]》中饰演旅行世界各地的奇獸飼育家[[紐特·斯卡曼德|紐特·斯卡曼德]]，贏得許多人的好評。該片由《[[哈利波特|哈利波特]]》作者兼本片編劇[[J._K._Rowling|J. K. Rowling]]確認會延長演出至五部。

==個人生活==
